data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE UP TO 3% of the purchase price towards the Buyers closing costs!!!! HURRY AND BRING US AN OFFER! Come check out this beautiful gated townhome community. This well maintained 2-Bedroom, 2-1/2 Bathroom home welcomes you with a  Formal Living Room & Formal Dining Room with pass thru to kitchen. You will fall in love with this home once you walk through the front door. This floorplan has all bedrooms upstairs. There is a large kitchen open to the dining room. Appliances Included: Refrigerator, Dishwasher, Disposal, Range, Microwave, Washer & Dryer. There are plenty of Oak Cabinets, lots of counter space. There is tile flooring in the family room, dining room, kitchen and baths and carpeting in the bedrooms only.   The master bedroom features a large walk-in closet and a roomy master bath with garden tub. There is a separate laundry room located upstairs, very convenient. The community has a community pool. There is plenty of shopping and a number of new restaurants in the area. There is also a  Publix, Aldis, Wal-Mart, Home Depot & Lowes is just a few minutes away. Close commute to I-75 & The Crosstown Expressway an easy commute to Tampa. New Materials to be left with the house for updating:  4” baseboards,  Flooring with stair edging, Yale Combination Lock for front door, White paint, Painting pan and rollers, Towel rings for bathrooms, Sink Faucets, Toilet paper holders with roller, Shower faucet sets, LED light fixtures and Caulking.
